      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this dependable ride! It has plenty of character and has been a reliable companion on the road. While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years of service, it still runs well and is ready for its next chapter. Perfect for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a great value!",
      "price": 19500.0,
